      <p style="line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Welcome to <strong>Wonta Rural Development Association</strong>.
      </p>

      <p style="line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 40px;">
        Dedicated to education, healthcare, empowerment, and sustainable agriculture.
      </p>
    </section>

